EX NO 7(B): ::  C PROGRAM TO DISPLAY HARDWARE DETAILS SUCH AS PRICE,PRODUCT NAME AND PRICE USING STRUCTURE.


AIM:
To write a program to display hardware details using structure.

ALGORITHM:
1. Start.
2. Define a variables.
3. Write a program to display hardware details such as price, product name and price
using structure.
4. Read the value using scanf.
5. Ask the user to make an input.
6. Print out the answer.
7. End.




PROGRAM:
#include<stdio.h>
struct hardware
{
char qr[10];
char product[10];
int price;
}j[10];
int main()
{
int i;
for(i=0;i<3;i++)
scanf("%s%s%d",j[i].qr,j[i].product,&j[i].price);
for(i=0;i<3;i++)
printf("QRcode:%s\nproduct:%s\nprice :%d\n",j[i].qr,j[i].product,j[i].price);}

C program to display hardware details using structure.



